Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.30,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,(飯田橋站)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.73,0:00:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼快就碰到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.23,0:00:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.54,0:00:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,碰到之後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.94,0:00:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,對不對啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.64,0:00:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼是這個?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.84,0:00:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼是這裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.34,0:00:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，我也覺得很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.97,0:01:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.77,0:01:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,還在那邊，在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.78,0:01:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,什麽鬼呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.38,0:01:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,有點不太一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.28,0:01:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是有點不一樣，對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.38,0:01:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.49,0:01:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼還挺棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.40,0:01:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,這一邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,用那個黑絲襪那個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.41,0:01:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯左邊那一個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.32,0:02:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,身材還不錯其實
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.93,0:02:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是那一個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.86,0:02:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯不小心撞到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.36,0:02:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯不要緊不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝了真的是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,往這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.58,0:03:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.48,0:03:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我們在拍攝所以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.48,0:03:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,這個臉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.59,0:03:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,可以稍微聊一下嗎?就是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.69,0:03:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,還挺不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,會有點不妙嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,挺不妙的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，臉上好像有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是厄不知不覺那個什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.90,0:03:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那是啊，那就把那個相機\N然後就變成這樣的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.80,0:03:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,目前還沒有使用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.01,0:03:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,所以只是會亮而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪裡現在?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.81,0:03:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去跟朋友見面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.01,0:03:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟朋友會合是吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.12,0:03:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.12,0:03:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,在什麼地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.02,0:03:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是店裡面嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.72,0:03:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,一起嘛一起-冰淇淋店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.82,0:03:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子有點餓，是不是啊?\N是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.23,0:03:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,確實會有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是很緊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我們就先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但一個人兩個人沒什麼區別
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.74,0:04:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我在做探訪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.44,0:04:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,因為你很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.74,0:04:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,所以就
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.94,0:04:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到沒有動怎麽樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.35,0:04:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣感覺?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.05,0:04:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是吃飯為止的時間還有嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.95,0:04:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以有段空閑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那真的可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,因為這邊很一是啊挺冷的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,就感覺那個-有一點的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.06,0:04:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,就放鬆點就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.06,0:04:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也會有酬勞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要移動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.47,0:04:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,很近嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.47,0:04:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-很近嗎?-那很近的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.37,0:04:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,就在這一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.58,0:04:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,這一邊嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.48,0:04:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,有點在意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.88,0:04:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼就稍微的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.48,0:04:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,去附近一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.88,0:04:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊也挺冷的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,看可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.49,0:04:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,如果很近的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,還挺那個的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,很奇特吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-剛剛-很可疑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.61,0:05:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,就在這一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.51,0:05:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,開始探訪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,很近吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.82,0:05:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,還挺近的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.52,0:05:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,有多少是不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不到一個小時
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.02,0:05:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,沒辦法，要約人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,應該是在這附近吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.43,0:05:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,吃什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.54,0:05:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯， 還沒有決定好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.54,0:05:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,涮火鍋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,哇這個牛逼啦\N好像很好吃的樣子，真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.64,0:05:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,搞得我們也肚子餓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.24,0:05:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.84,0:05:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要拍完了去吃?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.65,0:05:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,反正從我們從早搞到晚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.45,0:05:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.55,0:05:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我們這是做工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,很辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.66,0:06:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,可以嗎這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那你要推薦嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-竟然難得-我們都沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.86,0:06:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,啥啥啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.96,0:06:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那這樣就不要緊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.77,0:06:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,就是感覺有點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.37,0:06:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,像朋友的感覺不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.67,0:06:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣朋友就不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.07,0:06:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是很親人近人的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.08,0:06:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊是啊，我覺得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.38,0:06:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我們可以問下你名字嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫艾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.48,0:06:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,艾娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.98,0:06:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你多大了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,23歲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.18,0:06:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,哇很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.29,0:06:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺有點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯很成熟的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.59,0:06:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,還以為是學生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,之前還是學生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.20,0:06:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,現在也是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.90,0:06:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,哦這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.31,0:06:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你這麼說有點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,確實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:06:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,拿的東西也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.01,0:06:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你好像在看鐘的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.51,0:07:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.62,0:07:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,各位可以看一下嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.12,0:07:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,做什麼樣子的?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好像很貴的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.62,0:07:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好像很有錢的樣子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你做這個多久了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.63,0:07:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,一直都在做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.63,0:07:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,很還挺那個是吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.64,0:07:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,就是像酒一樣\N嗯，是啊，是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.24,0:07:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,有沒有什麼客人比較奇怪的?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.54,0:07:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,都是很普通的客人嗎?\N是的，沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.35,0:07:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子是吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,有點想去俱樂部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.75,0:07:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到如果有的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.26,0:07:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,這個俱樂部的話感覺有點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.76,0:07:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,經常會來嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,沒怎麼來過其實
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.46,0:07:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,偶爾來吃飯時候逛一下對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:07:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,會不會很貴的樣子?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.57,0:07:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,會不會一小時幾萬塊錢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.87,0:08:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有那麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,像這樣還是沒有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,一小時幾十萬太誇張了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣子的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.28,0:08:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我們都是這樣的印象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.58,0:08:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺像那些小大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，你們想多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.29,0:08:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那之前跟朋友去的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,哦發生什麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.09,0:08:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,然後唉難受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,只有這一點嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,一般不會那麼誇張的價格
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.40,0:08:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.80,0:08:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你看嘛，可樂那些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.10,0:08:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,之前還發生過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.51,0:08:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，那個唉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不知道怎麼組織語言
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那個我們不是進店嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那個小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.32,0:08:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,AV
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.52,0:08:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,但是av女優那樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想哇，真的假的呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，這是我最喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.72,0:08:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,這個剛好有我喜歡的橘色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.33,0:08:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,當時我們都蒙蔽了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.53,0:08:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,就是說AV女優在席的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.63,0:08:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼講呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,懂嗎這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.24,0:09:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,就是像那樣的店鋪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.64,0:09:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,對對對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,啊有這樣說過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,然後多少錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他就說9萬-好貴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.85,0:09:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是把9000讀錯了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.55,0:09:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,9萬9萬嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.46,0:09:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,然後然後出來之後\N我不知道你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.26,0:09:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,就是很貴嗎?那個錢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，我還是認識很多女優的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.66,0:09:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但是還出現了很多沒聽說過的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼樣的人?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.57,0:09:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,就是普通的阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.27,0:09:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,都三十歲的都有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.67,0:09:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,基本上都是那樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是聽說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.48,0:09:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,還什麼檢查過的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.28,0:09:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是9萬哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.08,0:09:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但是技術不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.38,0:09:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,技街怎麼樣啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.88,0:09:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.49,0:09:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不就是那樣的店鋪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:09:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不就是普通的陪酒女嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你們店鋪本身怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.40,0:10:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,歌舞伎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.50,0:10:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,可以說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.40,0:10:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,如果可以的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,多少才可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.30,0:10:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你是說出演嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.91,0:10:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但是這樣子看的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.81,0:10:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,有點可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.01,0:10:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,5000元握住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-做不到的呢一是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,完全做不到嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.32,0:10:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,5000元太少
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那1萬呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,1萬 也不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.43,0:10:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,三萬的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.43,0:10:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,而且還是不提要求的情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼都不被拜記也要嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-就只是接待嗎-差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.73,0:10:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,就是聊聊天?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,-那你說個時間一一小時
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.14,0:10:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,一小時啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.04,0:10:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,兩萬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.74,0:10:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,時間不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.84,0:10:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,因為這個酬勞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.65,0:10:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微有一點那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.35,0:10:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你說是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.95,0:10:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,今天休息嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.25,0:10:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.95,0:10:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那就可以一不用給了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.85,0:11:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.46,0:11:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然也沒有酒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.86,0:11:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,這個還是要好好接客才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.07,0:11:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你男友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.07,0:11:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.17,0:11:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.37,0:11:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但是工作上不是會認識很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.97,0:11:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,從那裡發展之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.68,0:11:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.98,0:11:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好真實
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.48,0:11:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然不是那樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.98,0:11:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,也是我朋友的店鋪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.68,0:11:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友?-像朋友那樣的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.58,0:11:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.89,0:11:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,多少了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,沒多久
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊20代沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.39,0:11:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,10代後半吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不發展對象
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.70,0:11:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼樣的人是類型
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,頭腦聰明聊天愉快的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.61,0:11:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,頭腦好是指學歷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.41,0:11:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.01,0:11:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,就是要單純的頭腦好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,思維敏捷的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣會可靠點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.42,0:12:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,對哦還有要積極的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.02,0:12:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,就是想要被教很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.73,0:12:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,年長也行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.53,0:12:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,都ok的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,像這樣子我覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.23,0:12:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,有沒有被說過?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.44,0:12:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,這個大家沒有聽過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,第幾次的約會?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.95,0:12:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,這可以上床
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,交往之後吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有興趣的話怎麼都不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.66,0:12:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,這倒是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.26,0:12:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,大概就是順其自然吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.26,0:12:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.06,0:12:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,一般要交往多久
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,印象好的話，第1次也可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,三次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.57,0:12:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,三次是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.07,0:12:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.87,0:12:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,還要多測試一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.87,0:13:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那就來個三次約會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,三次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.08,0:13:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,三次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,大都這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.88,0:13:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.08,0:13:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那一對面可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.19,0:13:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,只要順利的話就可以繼續是吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果可以的話，
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,兩次也是三次也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,說的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,三次的時候就已經
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.69,0:13:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,相當於是交往了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.60,0:13:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.30,0:13:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那一天也是0K的意思嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.10,0:13:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不會有第四次的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不會有第四次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.30,0:13:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,所以第三次是勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.11,0:13:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,第三次就會表露出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你的話是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.31,0:13:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,三次都還不行的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.02,0:13:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是沒戲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.02,0:13:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,基本上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,三次就可以決定 是吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.42,0:13:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我是這樣說的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.23,0:13:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.53,0:13:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,社會人都是這樣子的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.33,0:13:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,一般不會自己提出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.74,0:14:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,去這樣的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.04,0:14:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.94,0:14:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然會去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.54,0:14:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但是不怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.35,0:14:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,最近呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.85,0:14:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,沒怎麼跟別人見面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.95,0:14:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.15,0:14:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,今天不也和朋友出來玩嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.86,0:14:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,平時休息去哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.06,0:14:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,在家裡面平時
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.06,0:14:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,追劇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.36,0:14:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是什麼樣的視頻?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-是不是av啊一不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,-怎麼樣的-電影之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,電影電視劇?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好像你很習慣攝像機啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.88,0:14:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,只是拍是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,這不用介意的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,現在這樣的話嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.59,0:14:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,臉這邊之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.49,0:14:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,在近的地方-沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.79,0:15:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是很好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,今天還是精心打扮了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.70,0:15:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎都是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.70,0:15:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊好好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.50,0:15:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,處理的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.81,0:15:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,可以摸一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,坐就可以了吧一是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.51,0:15:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,這麽直接嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.31,0:15:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是沒有摸過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,還是十分的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.72,0:15:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.72,0:15:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.62,0:15:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,用點那個會好點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.62,0:15:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.72,0:15:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,就是想要弄點小小的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.52,0:15:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,靠近點看還是很漂亮的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我化了點小妝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.93,0:15:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那種很普通的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.93,0:15:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,直接弄在臉上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.54,0:15:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,眉毛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,眉毛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.74,0:15:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.65,0:15:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你想問什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.15,0:15:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你想問什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.85,0:15:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,靠近點不是會好點嘱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:15:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:16:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,像這檬的感覺也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.15,0:16:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,一直都在摸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,太靠近了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但是很可愛很漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.46,0:16:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊很漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,感謝一下你的王牌實力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,太難為情了 很難見到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好難為情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.27,0:16:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,美瞳很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺你很習慣攝像機
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.48,0:16:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.28,0:16:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.69,0:16:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,在這邊是吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.49,0:16:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,這個距離很近了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.69,0:16:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊有點像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.59,0:16:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有人靠過這麼近吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,太近了一是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.30,0:16:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,很熱很熱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,夾克脫了可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,臉還是挺近的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不嫌棄的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.51,0:16:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,包包放這裡吧一不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.31,0:16:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.81,0:16:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,看起來很貴不願意讓我們摸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.61,0:16:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我幫你脫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.02,0:17:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,脫了放那邊就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,隨便放一邊就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.72,0:17:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,放那裡就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.73,0:17:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊放這邊嗎啊，\N可以的，可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.23,0:17:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.73,0:17:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,多久做過一次啊?\N已經不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.04,0:17:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,猜猜看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.34,0:17:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,三天前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.84,0:17:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,最近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.64,0:17:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,搞過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.45,0:17:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,難道不是搞了才那麼漂亮的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.85,0:17:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是啊你說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,這也是有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.75,0:17:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,性感是最好的尤物是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.15,0:17:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,完全
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.65,0:17:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,真的假的?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.26,0:17:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢你說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.86,0:17:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是那個?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.36,0:17:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-就是客人之類的-沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.66,0:17:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.87,0:17:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,和別人也會這樣子嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.97,0:17:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,這個要看是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.07,0:17:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,果然還是看臉嗎? ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.07,0:17:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,有的話還是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.68,0:18:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好像很開心的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.68,0:18:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼時候?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.68,0:18:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.88,0:18:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.28,0:18:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.89,0:18:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,這個就是箱根那一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.39,0:18:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,這是浴室嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.19,0:18:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊是溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.79,0:18:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是只有温暖的地方才會有的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.29,0:18:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就是啊\N好像很開心的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.00,0:18:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,就是像這樣子才舒服啊\N嗯，這是混浴所以要戴面罩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.80,0:18:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼要戴面罩啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.20,0:18:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,這個好像很不錯哎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.30,0:18:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這個也沒有後天嗎?不有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.00,0:18:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣子嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你搞什麽剛剛那個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.41,0:18:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但是如果直接推倒的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.81,0:18:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,說不定可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.12,0:18:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.02,0:18:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,很惡心吧是吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,但是看起來很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.22,0:18:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,確實有點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.12,0:18:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是啊這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.22,0:18:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,游泳遊戲嗎還是說?泳衣有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我不怎麼會游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.43,0:18:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不過還是可以游一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.03,0:18:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.03,0:18:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,帶救生圈的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.83,0:18:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,有去過溫泉嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.93,0:18:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,還是很喜歡溫泉的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.63,0:19:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要一起去啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,現在沒什麼空
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.64,0:19:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你現在唉，總是有時間的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,順便去喝一杯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.14,0:19:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你請客嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.44,0:19:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,便利店不是也有嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.94,0:19:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,便利店裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,三件就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.85,0:19:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,然後把腳這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那就開始吧，一可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.36,0:19:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣子?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.36,0:19:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,來把手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.36,0:19:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,一手還是很溫暖的，一是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子很不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.88,0:19:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,應該有很多男性經驗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,也算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,經常跟他們一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.78,0:19:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.18,0:19:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,看這樣子比較容易健談
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.28,0:19:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,對對對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.39,0:19:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,所以男朋友才
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,所以轉瞬即逝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:19:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯不過這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.79,0:19:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,也不可避免啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,原來是這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.40,0:20:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,哈過獎了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,現在那個有各種各樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.11,0:20:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,時間不要緊吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.01,0:20:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,有點不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.91,0:20:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不會吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.91,0:20:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們就快一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.21,0:20:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是已經混熟了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.52,0:20:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.72,0:20:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,果然我還是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.92,0:20:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才我的意思你應該明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.43,0:20:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,還10分的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.03,0:20:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,H
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.63,0:20:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,會不會有點強硬?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.43,0:20:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就是最喜歡的男人之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.83,0:20:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,課程中應該也會有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.14,0:20:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,最近身持場，想了解一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.14,0:20:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.24,0:20:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.14,0:20:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,又沒有什麼什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.74,0:20:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就是一夜情也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.25,0:20:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,炮友有嗎?-有的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.75,0:20:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-有幾個-有兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.95,0:21:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,居然有兩個，還有誰呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.76,0:21:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不說我們也不知道是誰呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.06,0:21:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,就是和朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.46,0:21:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,還有客人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.67,0:21:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,還有客人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.67,0:21:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,厲害了這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.77,0:21:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,最近沒有搞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.97,0:21:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,和客人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.07,0:21:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,和客人他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.67,0:21:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,和客人?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.08,0:21:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.98,0:21:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就自然而然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.99,0:21:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,像這樣子也會有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.59,0:21:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺最近有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.99,0:21:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,就是像這樣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒有印象
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,最後的h是在什麼地方做的?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.40,0:21:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,比如說酒店或野戰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.40,0:21:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,就是炮友的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.61,0:21:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,就是彼此之間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.61,0:21:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,說是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.11,0:21:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,變態什麼之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.11,0:22:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有試過
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.11,0:22:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.62,0:22:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,有沒有什麼東西呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.62,0:22:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是比較奇怪的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.82,0:22:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,綜合劑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.72,0:22:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,發什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.12,0:22:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你想說在家宅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.82,0:22:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,青奸嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.13,0:22:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,有沒有試過?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.93,0:22:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,還是說這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.63,0:22:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,鄉下嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.13,0:22:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,一般什麼時候?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.53,0:22:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,深夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.84,0:22:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.24,0:22:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但是從3點開始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.24,0:22:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,大概就是那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.64,0:22:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,像這樣子的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.24,0:22:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,這禄子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.75,0:22:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,就是沒有到酒店嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.75,0:22:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那是怎麼搞的?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.95,0:22:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,本來是想要去酒店的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.46,0:22:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,後來中途想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.16,0:22:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,全部都做嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.46,0:22:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,全部
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.06,0:22:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.27,0:22:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-全部只是嗎就那樣嗎-是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.87,0:22:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不疼嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.57,0:22:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,後來就不疼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.37,0:22:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.07,0:22:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你這樣子的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.67,0:23:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對是從後面搞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.17,0:23:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,難道說抱起來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.88,0:23:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不然怎麼弄進去啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.38,0:23:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,確實是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.98,0:23:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但是如果是這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.98,0:23:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.08,0:23:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-怎麽了? -就是會弄亂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.59,0:23:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,還是很痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.59,0:23:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,弄了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.19,0:23:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，是啊，弄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.19,0:23:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,然後就停不下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.09,0:23:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,然後就煽風點雨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.19,0:23:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,然後就各種操作
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.50,0:23:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,就到此了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.70,0:23:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真的可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.40,0:23:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真的可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.20,0:23:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你想說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.90,0:23:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,可以起來一下嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.50,0:23:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,咱倆試一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.51,0:23:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,反正這邊是酒店
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.11,0:23:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你說對不對啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.51,0:23:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,這個床上不錯吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.81,0:23:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,時候有點那個
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.21,0:23:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.92,0:23:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我這邊的話有點
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.02,0:23:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微一點可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.12,0:23:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,假如說是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.53,0:23:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就稍微
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.03,0:23:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.73,0:24:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,可以坐下來嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.14,0:24:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下來是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.54,0:24:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,可以反過來摸嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.34,0:24:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧，這樣子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.55,0:24:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,來這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.05,0:24:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,這已經很
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.35,0:24:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.96,0:24:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.86,0:24:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊稍微再搞一點
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.66,0:24:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,反正也沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.66,0:24:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,看看
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.16,0:24:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,才還有5分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.46,0:24:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.47,0:24:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,摸摸可以給我看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.87,0:24:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,要給你們看嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.18,0:24:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我也會掏出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.58,0:24:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麽看呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.48,0:24:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.18,0:24:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.39,0:24:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.59,0:24:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.09,0:24:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,隨便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.89,0:24:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊一起嗎還是?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.89,0:25:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.60,0:25:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,時間也有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.20,0:25:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.90,0:25:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不要緊嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.81,0:25:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,可以稍微打個姿勢嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.51,0:25:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼東西?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.51,0:25:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,就是在哎這個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.32,0:25:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.92,0:25:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那一邊嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.22,0:25:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.93,0:25:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,一下就這邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.53,0:25:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,就像這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.73,0:25:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.34,0:25:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣還沒弄到吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.14,0:25:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.85,0:25:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡不是很厲害嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.05,0:25:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣子嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.75,0:25:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,幾次啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.05,0:25:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是裙子吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.95,0:25:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,這個期待嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.05,0:26:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.56,0:26:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.36,0:26:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這是內褲嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.16,0:26:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-水果內褲的味道-不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.06,0:26:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,內褲露出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.46,0:26:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,來這邊來搞
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.26,0:26:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,等一等內褲這個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.37,0:26:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,要看一下嘛，白內褲
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.47,0:26:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.37,0:26:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.28,0:26:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我這還沒有摸只是假裝
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.59,0:26:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,一抖一抖的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.19,0:26:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.90,0:26:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣?很不錯吧這個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.30,0:26:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.40,0:26:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.11,0:26:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.72,0:27:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,有點不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.92,0:27:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,有點不妙嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.32,0:27:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼東西不妙?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.52,0:27:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.62,0:27:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼不妙嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.82,0:27:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,這沒什麼吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.53,0:27:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,到酒店了還不行
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.23,0:27:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,哪邊?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.33,0:27:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,到哪一邊?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.83,0:27:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,要來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.43,0:27:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.94,0:27:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,可以接吻嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.74,0:27:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.04,0:27:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.55,0:27:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,只是稍微一點的話
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.05,0:27:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.55,0:27:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,前面
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.55,0:27:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,前面親吻
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.16,0:27:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,來來來
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.36,0:27:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,臉部面好紧張
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.26,0:27:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微有點黑
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.17,0:27:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好難為情的感覺是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.27,0:27:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.77,0:27:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,有點太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.77,0:28:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,很近嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.98,0:28:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.48,0:28:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.69,0:28:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,弄偏了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.89,0:28:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.49,0:28:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是心跳加速?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.29,0:28:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,估計還是很喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.70,0:28:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,搞得我像大叔一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.50,0:28:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.10,0:28:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,電停不下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.51,0:28:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,哇你看
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.71,0:28:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你看都弄到了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.72,0:28:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.12,0:28:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是搞到 了?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.22,0:28:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,等會兒等等
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.32,0:28:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,這個已經絕版了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.82,0:28:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,這個已經絕版了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.22,0:28:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這個已經絕版了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.33,0:28:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是這一附近嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.43,0:28:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.93,0:28:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣子嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.93,0:29:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,要弄嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.84,0:29:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,就幫我買一個
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.34,0:29:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,有錢的放心
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.54,0:29:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,30都準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.75,0:29:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,弄好就可以了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.15,0:29:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,先這樣子搞
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.85,0:29:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我就弄上
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.15,0:29:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,應該是搞不定的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.65,0:29:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那我來像這樣子就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.06,0:29:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,姑且還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.26,0:29:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.06,0:29:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.16,0:29:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊可以了吧，反正我會買的\N你要怎麼辦啊?真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.36,0:29:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我說真的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.87,0:29:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣就可以了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.87,0:29:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,這個是你的那個嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.87,0:29:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.87,0:29:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣這樣子的有嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.17,0:29:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.47,0:29:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好像很開心的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.57,0:29:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不要緊吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.08,0:29:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,很漂亮的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.28,0:29:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼內褲這個樣子啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.68,0:29:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,應該很貴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.98,0:29:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.79,0:29:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,這個顏色不錯是啊，
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.59,0:29:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,這個地方有一點高了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.19,0:29:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊弄出來
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.39,0:30:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是變了?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.09,0:30:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,渗透 了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.60,0:30:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.80,0:30:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.20,0:30:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,看得見
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.80,0:30:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.51,0:30:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不明白倒是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.31,0:30:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,可以接吻一下嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.71,0:30:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微檢查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.41,0:30:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,開始檢查還是檢查?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.31,0:30:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好難為情啊 說不定是很不妙的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.32,0:30:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,相機的話這邊那個
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.82,0:30:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,有點不喜歡相機
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.43,0:30:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就收斂一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.03,0:30:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微稍微
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.14,0:30:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,安靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.05,0:30:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,等等等等
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.45,0:31:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不沒有拍到臉沒有拍到臉
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.55,0:31:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.86,0:31:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.06,0:31:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.46,0:31:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,只是稍微弄一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.66,0:31:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你在觀察嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.27,0:31:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要舔啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.97,0:31:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.47,0:31:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那個有那個嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.87,0:31:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.87,0:31:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,-那個什麽之類的-有那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.08,0:31:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這一邊嗎?這邊也還是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.58,0:31:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,這個挺不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.68,0:31:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是這邊嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.20,0:31:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉，這一邊的你
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.91,0:31:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣行不行啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.81,0:31:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,可以可以
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.51,0:31:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你你這樣就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.81,0:32:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.31,0:32:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,反正也沒有相機
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.22,0:32:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那個人的話怎麼說呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.62,0:32:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不要紧不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.23,0:32:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,交給我吧好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.23,0:32:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,弄開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.84,0:32:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,很難為情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.74,0:32:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,難為情
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.94,0:32:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是很刺激吧，對不對?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.75,0:32:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,想要嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.35,0:32:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-不要緊的一大概在這跗近吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.35,0:32:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,對就是這一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.86,0:32:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是性感帶?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.56,0:32:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不要紧不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.16,0:32:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.37,0:32:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.97,0:33:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好興奮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.38,0:33:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,來這邊也來搞一下
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.59,0:33:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.59,0:33:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這個絕對可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.30,0:33:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.71,0:33:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,一很難為情嗎?一是的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.03,0:33:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,這摸的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.83,0:34:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,有反應嗎?說小一點
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.44,0:34:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,再稍微一點
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.04,0:34:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,會讓你舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.14,0:34:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,到這邊來一點
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.75,0:34:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事，這樣就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.85,0:34:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.05,0:34:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.86,0:34:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧，這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.38,0:34:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.10,0:35:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子不是不行吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.81,0:35:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,來來來這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.41,0:35:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-還有這樣的東西一不妙嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.51,0:35:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.42,0:35:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,超性感的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.52,0:35:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,來來來
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.42,0:35:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麽?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.23,0:35:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,已經看到脸了，不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.63,0:35:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,一邊看著臉，一邊那樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.54,0:35:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,就剛剛進到那邊那個你
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.35,0:36:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,來弄一下
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.44,0:37:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,粘乎乎的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.45,0:37:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.35,0:37:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,粘乎乎的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.95,0:37:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊弄髒了，有點不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.46,0:37:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,很熟
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.56,0:37:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,很熱吧，好多汗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.37,0:37:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊來一點
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.37,0:38:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,變成什麼樣子等等
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.58,0:38:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那這樣就可以了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.78,0:38:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,像這樣子的話
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.49,0:38:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-色情嗎一不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.09,0:38:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊牙弄一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.20,0:38:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我會的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.20,0:38:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊也弄到了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.61,0:38:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.21,0:38:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.02,0:38:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.42,0:38:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊好像會弄髒的樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.22,0:38:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好像已經弄到了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.72,0:38:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯稍微一點
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.43,0:38:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,先弄到一半吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.43,0:38:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,用一半
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.74,0:39:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微一點
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.74,0:39:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣可以吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.55,0:39:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,像這樣可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.57,0:39:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害這個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.18,0:39:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.58,0:39:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,變好一點就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.28,0:39:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.18,0:39:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,難道不是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.29,0:39:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊好像還是很明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.50,0:40:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,來這一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.51,0:40:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,來來來
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.41,0:40:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你的感想
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.52,0:40:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,看得見嗎看得見
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.42,0:40:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,來來這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.75,0:40:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.77,0:41:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,哇，這個有點厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.99,0:41:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.99,0:41:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣可以吧，這樣可以吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.00,0:41:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.80,0:41:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我來幫你弄一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.81,0:41:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了嗎?已經
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.01,0:41:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.82,0:42:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什麼啊，真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.92,0:42:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,一邊說不願意搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.42,0:42:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,這怎麼行呢?搞什麼的事?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.43,0:42:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺有點那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.13,0:42:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,有點舒服的東西出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.43,0:42:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.73,0:42:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.13,0:42:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,就是各種各樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.04,0:42:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什麼這是
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.34,0:42:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊是啊，在搞什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.34,0:42:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是吃飯嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.54,0:42:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,像這樣不就可以了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.65,0:42:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我剛剛說的吧，那個忘記的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.25,0:42:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,兒子夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.95,0:42:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,還可以的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.95,0:42:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你說是吧稍微
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.26,0:42:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,有可能會弄髒，所以
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.56,0:42:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣子吃飯的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.86,0:42:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是瘦瘦的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.37,0:42:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼遊戲?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.57,0:42:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.77,0:43:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那這樣就可以了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.38,0:43:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,應該不難為情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.68,0:43:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,很難為情
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.69,0:43:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,屁眼這邊也是
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.69,0:43:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.49,0:43:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,像這樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.50,0:43:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊也是
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.44,0:44:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,有沒有一種爽快的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.44,0:44:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好難為情
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.34,0:44:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺到難為情的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.85,0:44:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,像這樣子可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.85,0:44:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,像這樣可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.06,0:44:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你會弄嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.56,0:44:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事坐下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.97,0:44:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,來這邊幫我搞一下
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.17,0:44:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.87,0:44:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒還沒
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.48,0:44:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,可以弄嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.49,0:45:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,弄滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.69,0:45:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,像這樣子還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.60,0:45:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣會不會更好?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.70,0:45:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.50,0:45:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.60,0:45:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.30,0:45:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吧這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.41,0:45:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那像這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.52,0:45:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,有點不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.44,0:45:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,實在是太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.55,0:45:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,來來來
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.45,0:46:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是很不妙嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.05,0:46:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,付麼什麼呢?什麼呢?不要緊不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.06,0:46:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微弄一下對不對?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.87,0:46:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼會那麼熟練?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.67,0:46:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,能再弄一下嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.88,0:46:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,確實很熟
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.18,0:46:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.78,0:46:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不這樣子就不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.59,0:46:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜歡這樣子的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.89,0:46:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好好弄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.50,0:46:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,很不好
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.21,0:46:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,來來來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.41,0:47:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麽樣?這樣的感想
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.62,0:47:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,要去嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.22,0:47:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那這邊也來一點
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.42,0:47:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,還挺不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.12,0:47:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,挺那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.03,0:47:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,對對對對
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.93,0:47:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,這是有點理想的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.13,0:47:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你不這樣子就不知道吧?一是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.84,0:47:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧，這一邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.34,0:47:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,經驗人數呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.74,0:47:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,!@#￥%&*&
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.14,0:47:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子在口交
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.64,0:47:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.45,0:47:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,各種各樣的感覺來了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.05,0:47:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,來坐這邊，坐這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.56,0:47:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,來好好來吧，對對對
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.96,0:47:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒啊，這樣子的話
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.57,0:48:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.18,0:48:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.09,0:48:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,來來來
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.99,0:48:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那我裡面真的不要緊嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.90,0:48:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.80,0:48:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子不要緊吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.91,0:48:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,就是奇怪的地方舔的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.81,0:48:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子也很色情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.12,0:48:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那不要紧不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.84,0:49:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.54,0:49:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好興奮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.15,0:49:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼停下來了?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.86,0:49:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你要怎麼搞?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.67,0:49:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你想你要弄個嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.27,0:49:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒有弄
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.58,0:49:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,來這邊也來
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.10,0:50:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你好好看一看
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.72,0:50:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,弄不開呀
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.52,0:50:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.22,0:50:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,還有這麼多那個
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.64,0:50:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,像這樣的感覺嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.45,0:50:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,像這樣子可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.35,0:51:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我來幫你弄一下用嘴巴
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.56,0:51:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你們稍微那麼弄一下
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.46,0:51:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以進去嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.37,0:51:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,來這邊來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.37,0:51:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,在床上
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.07,0:51:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,掉下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.68,0:51:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,可以弄進去嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.78,0:51:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不要緊的不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.78,0:51:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯也不怎麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.08,0:51:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那個怎麼說呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.79,0:51:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,要要去嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.59,0:51:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣就可以去了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.39,0:51:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,啊這麼有點驚訝
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.40,0:51:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺很有幹勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.11,0:51:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,做愛的話怎麼說呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.31,0:51:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我這邊的話
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.41,0:52:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是很快嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.12,0:52:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.42,0:52:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,來了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.33,0:52:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.73,0:52:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你在摸乳頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.74,0:52:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.54,0:52:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,還是别的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.54,0:52:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不要緊嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.44,0:52:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.26,0:52:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,來這邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.88,0:53:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.69,0:53:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,軟綿綿的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.73,0:54:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不要緊吧 不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.78,0:54:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,叫得出来嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.78,0:54:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣水行啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.39,0:54:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊也來一點嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.19,0:54:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.72,0:55:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,還挺厲害的，感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.82,0:55:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,還經常
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.63,0:55:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊都在來嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.83,0:55:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然平時不怎麽
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.03,0:55:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,來嘛，只是偶爾不是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.23,0:55:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,拿來抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.84,0:55:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,來來
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.85,0:56:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.85,0:56:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.15,0:56:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,做的很棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.16,0:56:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.89,0:56:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,想變舒服嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.82,0:57:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣舒服嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.52,0:57:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.12,0:57:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.92,0:57:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,哪像這樣子的話
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.42,0:57:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.44,0:57:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.96,0:57:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.69,0:58:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,啊好淫蕩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.30,0:58:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,很不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.00,0:58:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.20,0:58:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,碰到了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.61,0:58:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧，先這樣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.11,0:58:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,來先這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.53,0:58:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害，這個腰都痛
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.74,0:59:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,很開心嗎果然是這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.14,0:59:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,現在這樣很不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.64,0:59:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,很難為情，確實會
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.54,0:59:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，很難為情
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.25,0:59:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子真的很漂亮啊,粘乎乎的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.45,0:59:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,想去嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.66,0:59:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,來來來
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.86,0:59:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,來這樣子可以吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.08,0:59:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.89,1:00:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害呀，带粽子
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.50,1:00:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,累了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.40,1:00:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣這樣子
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.23,1:00:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,很厲害哦，看到這個地方
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.84,1:00:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡這個嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.88,1:01:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,像這樣子可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.68,1:01:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.08,1:03:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.39,1:03:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,再靠近一點
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.29,1:03:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,弄到了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.69,1:03:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.21,1:03:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,像這樣可以吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.26,1:04:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.47,1:04:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,再來一下吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.73,1:05:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.43,1:05:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微-不是吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.13,1:05:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,今天還要去吃飯，不是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.54,1:05:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.96,1:06:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.27,1:06:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,再來一點了，很舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.97,1:06:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺你很不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.15,1:07:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.65,1:09:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.56,1:09:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.07,1:09:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.47,1:09:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.27,1:09:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊也很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.47,1:09:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,看看就可以吧
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.07,1:09:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是有一點
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.48,1:09:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我這邊才是要謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.38,1:09:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺有點厲害
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.88,1:09:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯,這樣子很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.08,1:09:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,色情是很色情啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.58,1:09:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我也很喜歡這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.39,1:09:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有這麼回事 很普通的
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.69,1:09:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,很害羞而已
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.09,1:09:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是的,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.29,1:10:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那還是很不錯的
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.69,1:10:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,做愛了啊,不要緊吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.89,1:10:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,既然難得再來,等一會兒吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.00,1:10:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,再再慢點也可以啊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.80,1:10:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,要回去了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.20,1:10:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,就這樣子吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.20,1:10:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.21,1:10:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,總之先
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.11,1:10:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,來先這樣子來吧，對對對對，就這樣子
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.91,1:10:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,因為很冷